Class LicenseValidator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.license4j.LicenseValidator

  • public class LicenseValidator
extends java.lang.Object
    LicenseValidator class provides license and serial number validation methods, and it is included in runtime library.

        Requests a floating license from given floating license server. Validation status can be obtained with getValidationStatus() method of License object. This is the new basic method to validate floating license text. Floating license server address must be given in the format ServerAddress:PortNumber. Instead of defining single floating license server, more than one server address can be defined separated with semicolon.

      • validateFloatingLicenseText

        public static License validateFloatingLicenseText(java.lang.String publickey,
                                  java.lang.String productID,
                                  java.lang.String productEdition,
                                  java.lang.String productVersion,
                                  java.lang.String serverAddress,
                                  FloatingLicenseCheckTimerHandler floatingLicenseTimerTaskHandler,
                                  java.lang.String additionalInfo)
        Requests a floating license from given floating license server. Validation status can be obtained with getValidationStatus() method of License object. This is the new basic method to validate floating license text. Floating license server address must be given in the format ServerAddress:PortNumber. Instead of defining single floating license server, more than one server address can be defined separated with semicolon. Method sends an additional information string to server and Floating License Server Administration GUI displays received string. String can be anything, max allowed length is 64. Strings longer than 64 characters in length will be truncated and first 64 characters will be sent to server.
        Parameters:
        publickey -
        productID -
        productEdition -
        productVersion -
        serverAddress -
        floatingLicenseTimerTaskHandler -
        additionalInfo -
        Returns:
        License object
